Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.70,0:00:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(拍摄地点  宇宙)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.11,0:00:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,银河天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.25,0:00:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(大家跟着一起唱吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.22,0:00:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你久等了  Everybody
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.39,0:00:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,HIGH  就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.89,0:00:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总是精神紧绷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.06,0:00:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论是波奇、老板\N帅哥或是上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.56,0:00:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.06,0:00:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假日上街买东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.07,0:00:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃到美味的试吃品  Lucky
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.74,0:00:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果想预约申请约会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.07,0:00:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随时接受登记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.41,0:01:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果想谈恋爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.75,0:01:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能只是一昧地追求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.75,0:01:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下就得靠神明帮忙保佑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.42,0:01:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切皆微笑以对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.09,0:01:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，笑一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.59,0:01:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,充满梦想的天使队  Guu
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.76,0:01:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轻轻松松毫不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.60,0:01:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都打平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.93,0:01:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凡事付之一笑  WAHAHA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.10,0:01:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要吃几碗请自便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.94,0:01:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃到饱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.27,0:01:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愿望是郊游旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.61,0:01:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狼吞虎咽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.44,0:01:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话题沸腾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.28,0:01:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超人气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.61,0:01:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我们身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.78,0:01:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熊、熊、熊猫\N熊、熊、熊猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.78,0:01:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熊、熊、熊猫\N熊、熊、熊猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.45,0:01:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来分个黑白是非吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.29,0:01:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切皆微笑以对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.56,0:01:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(火药味与烟草味的摩擦)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.53,0:01:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使还是老样子\N空荡荡的什么都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.24,0:02:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好歹也准备个房间的主人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.48,0:02:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两年没见面了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.02,0:02:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假装咳了一次咳嗽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.96,0:02:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后只再敲一次门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的好闲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.63,0:02:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯嗯，偶而悠闲地休息也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.91,0:02:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饶了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.41,0:02:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耳际一边听着青春腐烂的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.21,0:02:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要我如何悠闲地休息啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.94,0:02:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早知道会这样的话\N我也去请年假就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.15,0:02:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年假？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.38,0:02:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.75,0:02:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天一早突然请了年假呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.82,0:02:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是去约会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.32,0:02:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.79,0:02:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天有个男人打电话找佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.83,0:02:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说要在房间等她之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.50,0:03:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有啦\N我绝对没有偷听她讲电话喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.07,0:03:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真羡慕佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.40,0:03:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么好羡慕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.00,0:03:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我这个死党\N独自丢在不毛的沙漠不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.71,0:03:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.74,0:03:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她什么时候有的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.94,0:03:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.41,0:03:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去外面巡逻罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.78,0:03:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么要我去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.12,0:03:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当领航员啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.18,0:03:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.88,0:03:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然只想自己一个人幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝不让你如愿\N神明保佑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.49,0:03:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有在听吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.36,0:03:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么回自己房间\N还得被关在外面啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.07,0:03:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿健\N你要抱怨的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.30,0:03:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就抱怨自己的粗心大意吧\N不锁门就跑出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.44,0:03:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这是什么话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.94,0:03:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是去楼下的商店\N买些喝的东西而已耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.48,0:03:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寒酸的男人房间\N加上廉价酒的酒宴是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.78,0:03:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用这来招待突然找出来的女人\N未免太隆重了点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.22,0:03:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说话还是一样的苛刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.29,0:03:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.39,0:03:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是这一点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.09,0:04:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吸引我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.26,0:04:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.03,0:04:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离题了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.84,0:04:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是戒掉了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近开始重视身体健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽量不给自己多余的压力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.01,0:04:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工作呢？\N有继续在做吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.01,0:04:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，托你的福\N还有继续在做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.75,0:04:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别看我这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.35,0:04:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在士官学校的成绩\N可是第一名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.65,0:04:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以还不缺委托上门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真令人怀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.99,0:04:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那段在士官学校\N彼此较劲技术的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.03,0:04:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时候你的梦想是加入军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.77,0:04:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.37,0:04:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果没发生那个事件\N就不会离开学校…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，是我，你现在在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.42,0:04:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样子的，我们溜出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.68,0:05:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果方便的话\N要不要跟我们会合…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.65,0:05:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挂断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.29,0:05:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.46,0:05:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在她正忙着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.92,0:05:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别说废话\N立刻给我进行讯源追踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.46,0:05:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讯源追踪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.53,0:05:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然你以为我干嘛带你出来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.13,0:05:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.57,0:05:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想被扔出车外\N自己回去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我10秒钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.30,0:05:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后去了要做什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要给佛特一点颜色瞧瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.47,0:05:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人生不如意之事十之八九
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后呢，你想要说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.48,0:05:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要抽烟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是答应过我了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自从那事件以后\N你的肺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,约定是吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.49,0:05:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我是想问问你的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也会听别人的意见？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.63,0:05:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想让那些被你搞得头大的\N教官们听听啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧，我就听你说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.88,0:06:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讯源在前面的贫民街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.08,0:06:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贫民街…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.35,0:06:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光听这个名词\N似乎就感觉有股危险男人的香味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.58,0:06:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是现在我们并没有\N遇到危险跟不自由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.12,0:06:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是危险而是男人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.62,0:06:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不是不自由\N而是非常的不自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以请你专心看前面开车吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.49,0:06:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少在我们闪过\N长群婴儿车队的这段时间内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.23,0:06:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.66,0:06:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花好厉害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有一个人受伤耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.77,0:06:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有个大组织委托我一项工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你接受了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.64,0:06:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酬劳不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.78,0:06:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酬劳好到可把这当成最后一次\N然后到某处边境的行星隐居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.28,0:06:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要不要一起来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这玩笑太毒了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.65,0:06:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.32,0:06:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，不过早点洗手不干\N也是不错的计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.59,0:06:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我说完你的权利后\N将你铐上手铐的那天来临前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个玩笑也很毒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.83,0:06:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是说真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.80,0:06:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.90,0:06:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.57,0:07:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,委托人有点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.77,0:07:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托那家伙的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.91,0:07:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我即使抽一根烟\N也比国中时还要来得紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀了我的父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.82,0:07:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把溜出士官学校\N前去报仇的我的一个肺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.35,0:07:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泡到医院的甲醛水里的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.26,0:07:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么那家伙会找你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.56,0:07:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我现在使用假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他好像没发现是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你觉得如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.10,0:07:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不是该拒绝？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.60,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是已经决定了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打算接受委托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.30,0:07:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙的组织规模已经大到\N连军队也束手无策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.77,0:07:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今再去跟他抵抗\N然后以愚蠢的死状出丑，实在是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.94,0:07:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你决定那样做\N就随你高兴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.28,0:07:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.41,0:07:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目标是佛特修特伦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是你也可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.16,0:07:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说店里刚好没有客人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真走运呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.66,0:08:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明是花店\N卖的却只有仙人掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实在有点想不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.47,0:08:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，只有我被抛出车外\N毫发无伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系，我已经习惯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.94,0:08:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是距离目的地\N只剩两条街而已耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我们过了这两条街\N她就没命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.71,0:08:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，把脑袋洗干净\N等我来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.22,0:08:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然大致查过了屋内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到你竟然会用\N这种老套的招数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.99,0:08:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是所谓的"旧皮袋装新酒"吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.46,0:08:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,士官学校以来的决斗\N总算可以做个了断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.97,0:08:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话才说到一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若你的回答能让我满意\N我可以饶你一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.91,0:08:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你烦不烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.15,0:08:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,烦人的男人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惹人嫌…吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.52,0:09:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要抽烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.73,0:09:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要遵守规定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.26,0:09:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花，都搞定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.33,0:09:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟他们说\N我们不是来帮犯人逃狱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.67,0:09:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们都已经了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.28,0:09:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我下次一定不会再抽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去婉拒工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不过是要去拒绝工作的委托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.52,0:09:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那份见面礼也未免太重了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.39,0:09:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敢拒绝那家伙委托的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.82,0:09:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这世上\N我是第一个也是最后一个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.63,0:09:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟他之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.36,0:09:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直回避至今的故事\N终于到了该继续的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.84,0:09:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等你回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再让你多抽一根吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.41,0:09:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顺便两个人来喝个通宵如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.52,0:10:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋，事情没有那么轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.55,0:10:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.52,0:10:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我走罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.12,0:10:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,门不用锁\N窗户帮我关上就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.90,0:10:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.93,0:10:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家宠物店楼上就是目的地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.48,0:10:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.75,0:10:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.68,0:10:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后呢，后来怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少跟我打马虎眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.86,0:10:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开门见山地说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.46,0:10:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是男人跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.89,0:10:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是敏锐的兰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.23,0:10:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只顾自己一个人的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.13,0:10:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是你理所当然的报应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说的对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会洗心革面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.77,0:10:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.77,0:10:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么我们为了女人的友情\N干杯之后回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.11,0:10:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.61,0:10:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干杯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.78,0:11:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说到最近的车子\N和男人的没志气，实在是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.45,0:11:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思\N你们先回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.42,0:11:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.49,0:11:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早点回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.96,0:11:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特她怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.09,0:11:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓的好女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.69,0:11:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不轻易死心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这真的是最后一根罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.05,0:12:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉我，月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.15,0:12:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猴子的耳垂在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.06,0:12:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这真的是个谜题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.30,0:12:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明已经吃很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.37,0:12:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过点心却还吃得下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.37,0:12:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.38,0:12:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Bum  Bum  Bum  Bum  Bum  Bum
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.88,0:12:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天堂和降落伞都在天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.59,0:12:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要对那孩子Kiss\N对未来示出Peace
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.13,0:13:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,热热闹闹的每一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.73,0:13:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1  2  3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.77,0:13:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,展开你的双手  举起你的单脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摆出红鹤的姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.44,0:13:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你一起抱着新鲜的心情\N开心的去摘橘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.72,0:13:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,PPP  PPP  Happy

